  "texts": [
    "However, this trend is neither strict nor monotonic, as performance dips at higher ranks are also observed.",
    "This could possibly be due to a low intrinsic rank of ∆W being suffi- Table 7: Pre-multiplication vs Post-multiplication.",
    "cient to capture the transformation and higher ranks leading to over-parametrization rather than learning additional information.",
